# Services & Packages

## Adding a backend feature

1. Define Zod schema in `packages/api/src/schemas/`
2. Add route constant in `packages/api/src/routes.ts`
3. Extend `ApiClient` in `packages/api/src/client.ts`
4. Implement handler in the owning service (`auth`, `studio`, `admin`, `video-tools`, or `ai-content`)
5. Register proxy in `services/gateway/src/proxy/routes.ts` if new top-level path

## Service map

| Service | Owns |
|---------|------|
| `auth` | Account & security (login, register, JWT, me) |
| `studio` | Studio projects (CRUD, soft-delete, trash) |
| `admin` (`@vokop/admin-service`) | Admin RBAC, menus, users |
| `video-tools` | FFmpeg sessions, filmstrip jobs, editor apply/preview — uses `@vokop/pipeline` |
| `gateway` | Proxies `/api/v1/*` via `src/proxy/routes.ts` |
| `auth` | Login/register, RBAC, projects CRUD |
| `ai-content` (planned) | FunClip-inspired ASR, subtitles, LLM clip suggestions |

## video-tools patterns

- Use `@vokop/db` for Mongo/Redis; `@vokop/shared` for constants (never duplicate filmstrip/editor presets).
- **Sessions**: `sessionStore.ts` — upload once, TTL in Redis, file on disk.
- **Jobs**: `jobQueue.ts` — async work with progress; respect `MAX_FFMPEG_JOBS`.
- **Editor**: `src/editor/` — catalog, apply, FFmpeg preview; presets in `@vokop/shared/constants/editor.ts`.
- Validate responses with `toApiResponse(schema, data)` from `@vokop/api`.
- Handle `EADDRINUSE` with clear message; suggest `pnpm stop`.

## ai-content patterns (FunClip reference)

Reference: https://github.com/modelscope/FunClip

- Implement as **HTTP service** under `services/ai-content`, not Gradio.
- Prefer `sessionId` from video-tools for media input (no full re-upload).
- Long ASR/LLM work = **async jobs** + `GET /api/v1/ai/jobs/:id` progress (mirror filmstrip jobs).
- Outputs: timed transcript segments, SRT, optional `speakerId`, LLM clip ranges `[start, end]`.
- Gateway proxy: `/api/v1/ai` → `AI_CONTENT_URL`.
- Studio consumes results into timeline/captions; never embed FunClip UI.

## Package exports

- `@vokop/shared` — no React in main export; use `@vokop/shared/providers` for React providers.
- `@vokop/ui` — peer dep on React; Tailwind classes scanned via `@source` in `@vokop/tailwind-config`.
- `@vokop/tailwind-config` — shared Tailwind v4 entry (`@import "tailwindcss"`), UI package sources, and base styles. Apps import it once in their CSS entry.
- `@vokop/ui/antd` — Ant Design widgets + shared theme (`ThemeProvider`, tokens).

## Env

Root `.env` is loaded by all services. Key vars: `MONGODB_URI`, `REDIS_URL`, `GATEWAY_PORT`, `VIDEO_TOOLS_PORT`, `AUTH_PORT`, `AI_CONTENT_PORT`, `SESSION_TTL_SEC`.
